Build an *exhaustive* candidate list of **tiny, CPU-only rerankers released or updated after 2025-10-31**. This list is the **sole source of truth** for the reranker bake-off (new models only).

## Hard Filters (non-negotiable)
- Release/update date >= 2025-11-01 (`createdAt` + `lastModified`)
- CPU-only viable (ONNX/gguf/int8 or native CPU runtime)
- “Tiny” footprint: prefer <= 500M params or <= 500MB disk (quantized OK)
